        <briefdescription>
<para>Configure hardware pins for this input. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called by <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup_1a54bf0702b5027fc15906ca378515ad0b" kindref="member">PanelGroup::setup()</ref> after chip.init() completes. Call _pin.configureAsInput() here — not in the constructor — because MCP23017 register writes require chip.init() to have run first.</para>
<para>Default is a no-op. Override in every input class that owns a <ref refid="classPinRef" kindref="compound">PinRef</ref>. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
